title: ['POST-R-001 [18R649_010]']
characteristics_ch1: ['tissue: primary tumor (colorectum)', 'time point: post-treatment', 'treatment response: post-Tx non-PD']
extract_protocol_ch1: ['macrodisssection of an unstained FFPE tissue section, followed by total RNA extraction using TRIzol reagent.', 'A cDNA library was constructed using TruSeq RNA Access Library Prep Kit (Illumina, Inc., San Diego, CA, USA) and paired-end sequencing was conducted using an HiSeq 2500 platform (Illumina Inc).']
data_processing: ['All fastq format reads were assessed for quality control using FASTQC software (v0.11.8).', 'The Illumina sequencing platform-specific adaptors and poor quality read bases were trimmed using Trim Galore (v0.4.5).', 'The trimmed reads were mapped to the reference genome  with STAR aligner (v2.6.0) and the output sam/bam files were obtained.', 'Gene expression was quantified using RSEM (v1.2.23)', 'normalized through DESeq2 BiocManager package (v1.20.0)', 'Genome_build: GRCh38/hg38', 'Supplementary_files_format_and_content: comma-delimited text files include raw counts and FPKM values for each Sample']
